item.title: Why is Pwnscape V3 laggy for me?
item.dc:creator: @si_force Si Force
item.description:
@si_force wrote:

There has been servers hosted on 32mb of ram and having a capicity of 10 players, without any server-sided LAG, that is quite a good feat, so 5mb is good enough, the reason why your source would LAG is because Pwnscape is a very un-stable source.

Cleaning it out doesn’t mean just removing a few comments, it means sweeping through the whole thing, removing anything useless, removing everthing that isn’t vital, I am sure that server contains its fair share of useless code.
